{"tid":2074538,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"now發現垃圾銅芯口罩阿婆底褲部分隔層多次清洗後出現滲水","createTime":"2020-06-22T07:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T10:28:47.000Z","uid":236891,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"efe9b1a51269e7e484a32fbda948bc176bfe9349","tid":2074538,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:33:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395306&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395306%26refer%3DShare&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FyfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=d9c5cc92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395306%26refer%3DShare&h=cbad576b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=395306&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府浪費了八億，向市民派發銅芯口罩，創科局一共收到144萬宗市民登記。不過，我們委託大學進行測試發現，口罩部分的隔層經過多次清洗後，出現滲水情況，學者擔心影響防護能力。<br />\n<br />\n銅芯口罩，高官、特首出席場合都會戴上。不過，在街上戴的人並不算多。<br />\n<br />\n聲稱可以清洗六十次的銅芯口罩，經過多次清洗後，保護功能如何呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們將兩個口罩，根據說明書建議，用清水及梘液清洗，然後再放在陰涼的地方掠乾，將三個分別是沒有洗過、洗過三十次及五十次的口罩，送給中大通識教育基礎課程高級講師彭金滿博士，逐層將物料剪開，進行「潑水測試」。<br />\n<br />\n將一滴直徑0.1mm水滴滴在上面，表面的布料無清洗以及洗過30次的並無滲水，但洗了50次的口罩，水就滲了入布料內，學者擔心會影響保護性。<br />\n<br />\n至於濾芯的部分，我們亦逐層拆開進行測試。保護層方面，全新的口罩竟然有滲水，洗完30次及50次的就無；至於抗菌層，洗完30次及50次都有滲水情況。<br />\n<br />\n負責研發「銅芯口罩」的香港紡織及成衣研發中心9up，口罩外層布料不具備防水功能，防護設計是利用多層結構，而非以防水物料來阻隔飛沫；中間包裹的濾芯外層和抗菌層含微量銅，可抑制細菌、病毒和有害物質，過濾層就阻擋大部分微粒、細菌及飛沫。<br />\n<br />\n牠們建議市民主要用於日常生活防護，不建議生病時、照顧病人或在醫院診所等環境使用。"},{"pid":"fcffc1872720786fdbdeb4e688c8d79f4dc29435","tid":2074538,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"銅芯眼罩"},{"pid":"779a230a16ee8c07c10a0bbd02f47ddf774b8fbb","tid":2074538,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcffc1872720786fdbdeb4e688c8d79f4dc29435","tid":2074538,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:34:34.000Z","msg":"銅芯眼罩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"銅芯奶罩"},{"pid":"d2dad8f5dfdadd86f44020c0a9153a416c6fd5db","tid":2074538,"uid":144767,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 用果班人都可能唔知原來要洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9130f3a2d1d543b1e809e13c414c6bee49d23b46","tid":2074538,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"理鳩得你，錢已使"},{"pid":"4bcf7c758a0033bfb6d15e40cf9c4c173c67de5b","tid":2074538,"uid":125219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"政府搞得既創科都垃撚圾"},{"pid":"a8ba3d8c8d5530dab791af6f526d477a059ad86b","tid":2074538,"uid":249708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"代答：口罩獲國際認證出廠合格。<br />\n<br />\n新聞處女職員歡迎抄post"},{"pid":"2fbabaf9643f040e9578dbbd4415996445cc731a","tid":2074538,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"先頭唔係已經有一間報社check過話洗20次已經玩完咩，又多一間check佢定就係now<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ea53b823bee10cf8e9e048e82a5fde378ded75","tid":2074538,"uid":243677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9130f3a2d1d543b1e809e13c414c6bee49d23b46","tid":2074538,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"理鳩得你，錢已使"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:51:11.000Z","msg":"理鳩得你，錢已袋"},{"pid":"6201f563da22adc82131d1573a441ec34788ad2e","tid":2074538,"uid":357936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065c45ec603561e71ae0e97625a6572a07906d56","tid":2074538,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht